# CURSOR RULES — FOLDERA

`AGENTS.md` is the single agent execution contract for this repo. Read it and follow it exactly.

Boot sequence:

1. Read `ACTIVE_HANDOFF.md`.
2. Read the active issue it names.

One active seam only. PR-based workflow only. No direct edits to `main`. Source-truth closeout and a GitHub receipt are required before stop.
